{"tid":1651482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[注意] 連登冷氣軍師注意事項","createTime":"2019-10-13T11:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T11:15:03.000Z","uid":35485,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"79935ef29f25740f49e80e9b37877ec310e2fb76","tid":1651482,"uid":35485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:00:06.000Z","msg":"To do:<br />\n1. 睇直播嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">cap低被捕畫面</span></span></strong> 記低被捕手足講嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個人訊息</span></span></strong> 通知星火<br />\n2. 直播留意狗動向 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">喺tg group/ HKmap.live 提醒在場手足</span></span></strong><br />\n3. 對應黑警行動 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">可建議</span></span></strong>未來數小時抗爭方向 旁觀者清<br />\n4. 必要時<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">落街做街坊聲援</span></strong></span><br />\n5. 事後檢討<br />\n6. 網絡輿論戰 &amp; 製造文宣<br />\n<br />\nNot to do:<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">渲染負面情緒</span></strong> e.g. 慘敗 送頭<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌亂開po</span></strong> 分散注意<br />\n<br />\n**留意連登只係扮演[b]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輔助角色/工具</span></span>["},{"pid":"a4be884aa822cc2ed5a67addf7182240b8eedde3","tid":1651482,"uid":35485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:00:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b574ee4ae96cf52a1e956eaa118c1e083c206a21","tid":1651482,"uid":35485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:01:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"33a8e8aa31442435c6acc61823240ab9f0c05f9d","tid":1651482,"uid":35485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:01:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cfa7efabb86c51b6aca5adcd3f21f8d56cd5e35d","tid":1651482,"uid":35485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11: